    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "IMO that's very brittle logic that I'd rather have in the connector than in the widget, the one you linked seems like another implementation than the one in IS.js with Pagination.js. for exactly that reason I'd like to have this info in the connector. \r\n\r\nI think a good option would be to make a new connector, e.g. `unsafe_connectPagination()` which we add for now, can be used internally by our IS implementations, or simply adding the extra info under a `beta` name",
